                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 brand-font" style="color: #1E1E1E;">Redefining Modern Luxury</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed" style="color: #4A4A4A;">
                        At URBAN ÉLITE, we believe that true luxury is found in the intersection of exceptional craftsmanship and contemporary soul. Born from a vision to curate more than just products, we offer an invitation to a lifestyle defined by elegance and sophistication.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed" style="color: #4A4A4A;">
                        Our collections are hand-selected with meticulous attention to detail, ensuring that every piece resonates with the quality and style our community deserves. From timeless fashion to modern lifestyle essentials, experience the pinnacle of urban living.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-col">
                            <span class="text-3xl font-bold" style="color: #B76E79;">15k+</span>
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Elite Members</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-px h-12 bg-gray-200 mx-4"></div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col">
                            <span class="text-3xl font-bold" style="color: #B76E79;">200+</span>
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Curated Brands</span>
