                                <span class="ml-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white p-1.5 text-gray-900 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-sm border">
                                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line"></i>
                                </span>
                            </summary>
                            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                                Joining is simple. Create an account, set your style preferences, and you'll automatically be enrolled in our base membership. Elite tiers are unlocked through engagement and exclusive invitations.
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-[#FAFAFA] [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-6">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">How is product authenticity guaranteed?</h3>
                                <span class="ml-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white p-1.5 text-gray-900 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-sm border">
                                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line"></i>
                                </span>
                            </summary>
                            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                                Every item undergoes a multi-stage physical inspection by our master curators. We source directly from authorized dealers and provide a digital certificate of authenticity with every purchase.
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-[#FAFAFA] [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-6">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">What are the shipping costs for members?</h3>
                                <span class="ml-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white p-1.5 text-gray-900 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-sm border">
                                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line"></i>
                                </span>
                            </summary>
