                                Base members enjoy competitive flat rates. Premium tiers often qualify for complimentary priority shipping. You can view real-time estimates at checkout.
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-[#FAFAFA] [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-6">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">What is your return policy?</h3>
                                <span class="ml-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white p-1.5 text-gray-900 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-sm border">
                                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line"></i>
                                </span>
                            </summary>
                            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                                We offer a 14-day "No Questions Asked" inspection period. If the item doesn't meet your expectations, we'll arrange a priority pickup at your convenience.
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-[#FAFAFA] [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-6">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Is my payment information secure?</h3>
                                <span class="ml-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white p-1.5 text-gray-900 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-sm border">
                                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line"></i>
                                </span>
                            </summary>
