                                Absolutely. We use bank-grade 256-bit encryption for all transactions. Your sensitive data is handled via the "Secure Vault" protocol and is never stored on our primary servers.
                            </div>
                        </details>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

